{
  "stem": "2118.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my father didn't let us go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said no, you stay at home, and we don't run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We have more chance of survival at home under your roof than going to who knows where.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I'm not gonna go into the people who went, because I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, the war went on for-- till four weeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After four weeks, Poland capitulated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They had the guarantee that the soldiers who were being taken in Warsaw will not be taken to POW camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They will be released on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They will be free to go home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, my brother was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So my brother came home right away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He came home--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My bother Leibel, my oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was hit in the nose by a shrapnel, by a piece of shrapnel.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It cut his nose, and they just tied it on with-- with-- whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and it healed, and he went home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, after the war in Poland was over, which was four weeks, I don't remember how long, we received a letter from my other brother.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was in a POW camp in-- in a stalag.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember the number of the stalag.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They called it a stalag.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, they were not separated, the Jews from the Polish soldiers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were all-- and it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a couple letters, and then he came home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Now this was in '39.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In-- in-- in October, it was the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they announced that the Jews cannot pray on this holiday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was Rosh Hashanah and Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the temples were closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Temples were closed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You weren't supposed to pray at home, either.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
